div.p:
10 If thy body be dry, and such as a
Purgation will hardly worke withall;
thou must take the greater quantitie.

But the most easie and ready cure of the
Iaundise, is by the conserue for the Iaundise;
of which take euery morning fasting,
for ten dayes together, as much as a Walnut,
and fast one houre after it.
